  "body": "<center>\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KOz7JEb.png\" alt=\"Upgraded Core\">\n</p>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://files.minecraftforge.net/net/minecraftforge/forge/\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Forge-Only-d9aa6b?style=for-the-badge&logo=condaforge&logoColor=d9aa6b&labelColor=26303d\" alt=\"Forge Only\"></a>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7hyxts1.png\">\n</p>\nPlease use the Modrinth download and do not rehost the files.\n\nThis mod may be used in any modpacks. (On Modrinth)\n\n\nNo plan for fabric version at this time, sorry.\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7hyxts1.png\">\n</p>\n <u><b>DESCRIPTION</b></u><br><br><br>\n\nThis mod contains shared code for my other mods.\n\nThis mod doesn't do anything by himself. \n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7hyxts1.png\">\n</p>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-netherite\" title=\"Upgraded Netherite\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7seKMZeT/62d61f2a09ab2b71272ddf9b8ac0e941a2152399.png\" title=\"Upgraded Netherite\" width=\"64\"></a></td><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-netherite\"><b>Upgraded Nethrite</b></a><br>Adds upgraded versions of Netherite with helpful effects.</td></tr>\n<tr><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-netherite-items\" title=\"Upgraded Netherite : Items\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/x2OcOwHz/a390efeb5adc0ab6c2bf8738432d87f118073fa8.png\" title=\"Upgraded Netherite : Items\" width=\"64\"></a></td><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-netherite-items\"><b>Upgraded Netherite : Items</b></a><br>Adds some items like apples and totems to the Upgraded Netherite mod.</td></tr>\n<tr><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-netherite-ultimerite\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bcGOQ7CG/d0b6620ed4ad68af5639651cbe1e53f42e6fb10f.png\" title=\"Upgraded Netherite : Ultimerite\" width=\"64\"></a></td><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-netherite-ultimerite\"><b>Upgraded Netherite : Ultimerite</b></a><br>Adds Ultimerite Tier to the Upgraded Netherite mod.</td></tr>\n<tr><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-tools\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/g5wnyyqe/0107b4718248527938f12e19b1b0d06ab49d68db.png\" title=\"Upgraded Tools\" width=\"64\"></a></td><td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/upgraded-tools\"><b>Upgraded Tools</b></a><br>Add hammers that act as swords, axes, picks, shovels and hoes combined.</td></tr>\n</table>\n</center>",
